{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/cli-updatenotifier","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"6bd45e58-33bc-5deb-b0ee-d03575725e48","html":"<p>This is a series of libraries and utilities for building Command-line-interfaces aka CLI using Node.js and ecosystem around it. Similar utilities/helpers may be available for other languages but, these series is focused on JavaScript and its friends.</p>\n<p>You can check all articles under <a href=\"/category/cli-build-tool/\"><code class=\"language-text\">CLI Build Tool</code></a> tag.</p>\n<h2 id=\"update-notifier\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#update-notifier\" aria-label=\"update notifier permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://github.com/yeoman/update-notifier\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">update-notifier</a></h2>\n<p>If you are building a CLI that is based on npm ecosystem, i.e, installed via magical command called as <code class=\"language-text\">npm install</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">update-notifier</code> is a must utility that you must add in your CLI App. Nearly 3.5+ million packages are dependent on these library.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">update-notifier</code> inform users of your package of updates in a non-intrusive way.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/7a8f9/updatenotifier.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.83333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/8ac56/updatenotifier.webp 240w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/d3be9/updatenotifier.webp 480w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/e46b2/updatenotifier.webp 960w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/f992d/updatenotifier.webp 1440w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/882b9/updatenotifier.webp 1920w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/f98c2/updatenotifier.webp 2988w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/8ff5a/updatenotifier.png 240w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/e85cb/updatenotifier.png 480w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/d9199/updatenotifier.png 960w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/07a9c/updatenotifier.png 1440w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/29114/updatenotifier.png 1920w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/7a8f9/updatenotifier.png 2988w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/d9199/updatenotifier.png\"\n          alt=\"Screenshot\"\n          title=\"Screenshot\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>The best part of the utility is ease of use.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> updateNotifier <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'update-notifier'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> pkg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'./package.json'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">updateNotifier</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> pkg <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">notify</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Yes, thatâ€™s it. It will do the rest for you. There are some options available for more advanced usage but above code does all what you need.</p>\n<p>Whenever you initiate the update notifier, it will asynchronously check with npm in the background for available updates, then persist the result. The next time the notifier is initiated, the result will be loaded into the <code class=\"language-text\">.update</code> property. This prevents any impact on your package startup performance. The update check is done in a child process. This means that if you call process.exit, the check will still be performed in its own process.</p>\n<p>You can check out official <a href=\"https://github.com/yeoman/update-notifier\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">repo</a> for all usage details.</p>\n<p>Github Repo: <a href=\"https://github.com/yeoman/update-notifier\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">update-notifier</a></p>\n<hr>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/cli-updatenotifier","tagSlugs":["/tag/cli/","/tag/tools/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-06-24T18:05:00.738Z","description":"Node.js CLI App helper module for app update notification","tags":["CLI","Tools"],"title":"Tool of the Trade for CLI Apps - `update-notifier` ðŸ“®","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/cli-updatenotifier"}}}